With being steps away from Edmontons famous river valley and tons of amenities including one of Edmontons newest libraries, Bonnie Doon mall, and Argyll Learning centre this is a perfect opportunity for any investor or home owner looking to build their new home in the core of Edmonton.  30 X 120' (30450695)
